		icon: 'professional',
		date: 'Aug 2019 - July 2020',
		desc: 'Devising bespoke lineups for 11 cinemas in UK/Ireland to maximise revenue. \n Negotiating with film distributors and cinema management. \n Data analysis on box office performance. '
